    "result": {"data":{"cur":{"id":"72e4c937-a0cc-552c-b2a0-36847bf88c5d","html":"<h2 id=\"-safe-area\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-safe-area\" aria-label=\" safe area permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>✅ Safe Area</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 200%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"SafeArea\"\n        title=\"SafeArea\"\n        src=\"/static/b6aed86e5e1f92e89ff071a03a7200ae/37523/preview.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b6aed86e5e1f92e89ff071a03a7200ae/e9ff0/preview.png 180w,\n/static/b6aed86e5e1f92e89ff071a03a7200ae/f21e7/preview.png 360w,\n/static/b6aed86e5e1f92e89ff071a03a7200ae/37523/preview.png 720w,\n/static/b6aed86e5e1f92e89ff071a03a7200ae/ef6b9/preview.png 832w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span><br>\n<br>\n그림에 보이는 영역이 Safe Area에 해당한다. 기본적으로 SwiftUI에서는 뷰를 Safe Area 안에만 배치한다.</p>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"️-ignoressafearea\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EF%B8%8F-ignoressafearea\" aria-label=\"️ ignoressafearea permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>↕️ ignoresSafeArea()</h2>\n<p>= Safe Area 밖까지 뷰를 확장함 (Expands the view out of its safe area)</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 84.44444444444446%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"ignoresSafeArea\"\n        title=\"ignoresSafeArea\"\n        src=\"/static/e22e6a669d442c3b02d1fa684fffc5e0/37523/ignoressafearea.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e22e6a669d442c3b02d1fa684fffc5e0/e9ff0/ignoressafearea.png 180w,\n/static/e22e6a669d442c3b02d1fa684fffc5e0/f21e7/ignoressafearea.png 360w,\n/static/e22e6a669d442c3b02d1fa684fffc5e0/37523/ignoressafearea.png 720w,\n/static/e22e6a669d442c3b02d1fa684fffc5e0/302a4/ignoressafearea.png 1080w,\n/static/e22e6a669d442c3b02d1fa684fffc5e0/07a9c/ignoressafearea.png 1440w,\n/static/e22e6a669d442c3b02d1fa684fffc5e0/0ef7e/ignoressafearea.png 1594w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token comment\">// #1</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">HomeView</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">View</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> body<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">some</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">View</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token class-name\">ZStack</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token class-name\">Color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>blue\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token comment\">// #2</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">HomeView</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">View</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> body<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">some</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">View</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token class-name\">ZStack</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token class-name\">Color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>blue\n                <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">ignoresSafeArea</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// safe area 무시</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<br>\n다음 예시를 보면 Zstack 뷰를 body에 위치하고 배경색으로 파랑색을 설정하고 있다.  \n<br><br>\nignoresSafeArea()가 없는 경우 safe area에만 파란색 배경이 적용되지만, .ignoresSafeArea()를 사용하면 safe area 밖의 영역까지 파란색 배경이 적용되는 것을 확인할 수 있다.\n<p><br><br></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/documentation/swiftui/image/ignoressafearea(_:edges:)/\">애플 공식문서 : ignoresSafeArea(_:edges:)</a></p>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#-safe-area\">✅ Safe Area</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EF%B8%8F-ignoressafearea\">↕️ ignoresSafeArea()</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>","excerpt":"✅ Safe Area  \n그림에 보이는 영역이 Safe Area에 해당한다. 기본적으로 SwiftUI에서는 뷰를 Safe Area 안에만 배치한다. ↕️ ignoresSafeArea() = Safe Area 밖까지 뷰를 확장함 (Expands the view out of its safe area)   애플 공식문서 : ignoresSafeArea(_:edges:)  ✅ Safe Area ↕️ ignoresSafeArea()","frontmatter":{"date":"April 08, 2022","title":"Safe Area와 ignoresSafeArea() 이해하기 - SwiftUI","categories":"iOS","author":"콤퓨타샤","emoji":"📱"},"fields":{"slug":"/iOS-SafeArea/"}},"next":{"id":"2ec10e0f-217f-5b70-b7af-e933ec63300a","html":"<h2 id=\"피츠의-법칙fitts-law\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%94%BC%EC%B8%A0%EC%9D%98-%EB%B2%95%EC%B9%99fitts-law\" aria-label=\"피츠의 법칙fitts law permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>피츠의 법칙(Fitts’ Law)</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 73.88888888888889%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"피츠의 법칙\"\n        title=\"피츠의 법칙\"\n        src=\"/static/dcb882b79ac842648ad738a80b5a65ad/37523/fitts.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dcb882b79ac842648ad738a80b5a65ad/e9ff0/fitts.png 180w,\n/static/dcb882b79ac842648ad738a80b5a65ad/f21e7/fitts.png 360w,\n/static/dcb882b79ac842648ad738a80b5a65ad/37523/fitts.png 720w,\n/static/dcb882b79ac842648ad738a80b5a65ad/302a4/fitts.png 1080w,\n/static/dcb882b79ac842648ad738a80b5a65ad/07a9c/fitts.png 1440w,\n/static/dcb882b79ac842648ad738a80b5a65ad/3d22e/fitts.png 2010w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"-개요\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EA%B0%9C%EC%9A%94\" aria-label=\" 개요 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>💁🏻 개요</h3>\n<p><strong>대상에 도달하는 시간은 대상까지의 거리와 대상의 크기와 관련있다.</strong></p>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"️-요점\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EF%B8%8F-%EC%9A%94%EC%A0%90\" aria-label=\"️ 요점 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>☝️ 요점</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>터치 대상의 크기는 사용자가 정확하게 선택할 수 있을 정도로 커야 한다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>터치 대상 사이에 충분한 거리가 필요하다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>터치 대상은 쉽게 도달할 수 있는 영역에 배치해야 한다.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"-엄지-영역the-thumb-zone\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EC%97%84%EC%A7%80-%EC%98%81%EC%97%ADthe-thumb-zone\" aria-label=\" 엄지 영역the thumb zone permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>👍 엄지 영역(the Thumb Zone)</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64.44444444444444%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"엄지 영역\"\n        title=\"엄지 영역\"\n        src=\"/static/1275bed54766b3496bbc5ab8c960f4fb/37523/thumb-zone-mapping-opt.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1275bed54766b3496bbc5ab8c960f4fb/e9ff0/thumb-zone-mapping-opt.png 180w,\n/static/1275bed54766b3496bbc5ab8c960f4fb/f21e7/thumb-zone-mapping-opt.png 360w,\n/static/1275bed54766b3496bbc5ab8c960f4fb/37523/thumb-zone-mapping-opt.png 720w,\n/static/1275bed54766b3496bbc5ab8c960f4fb/6bff2/thumb-zone-mapping-opt.png 957w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<p>한 손으로 스마트폰을 사용할 때 엄지손가락을 편안하게 뻗을 수 있는 영역을 보여주는 다이어그램.<br>\n<strong>왼손 사용자와 오른손 사용자 모두에게 자연스러운 영역</strong>이 사용자를 위한 최적의 영역이다. (중간에 위치한 다이어그램)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.smashingmagazine.com/2016/09/the-thumb-zone-designing-for-mobile-users/\">이미지 출처</a></p>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%ED%94%BC%EC%B8%A0%EC%9D%98-%EB%B2%95%EC%B9%99fitts-law\">피츠의 법칙(Fitts’ Law)</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#-%EA%B0%9C%EC%9A%94\">💁🏻 개요</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EF%B8%8F-%EC%9A%94%EC%A0%90\">☝️ 요점</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#-%EC%97%84%EC%A7%80-%EC%98%81%EC%97%ADthe-thumb-zone\">👍 엄지 영역(the Thumb Zone)</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"date":"February 20, 2022","title":"피츠의 법칙, 엄지 영역","categories":"UX/UI","author":"콤퓨타샤","emoji":"🖥️"},"fields":{"slug":"/UX-Fitts-Law/"}},"prev":{"id":"767aea87-aeb2-5ef5-8f99-e28fcac0a81d","html":"<h2 id=\"-vstack\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-vstack\" aria-label=\" vstack permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>🥞 VStack</h2>\n<p>child 뷰를 수직으로 정렬하는 뷰</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 254.44444444444449%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"VStack\"\n        title=\"VStack\"\n        src=\"/static/b1ec75b62d9ad30329f3f64d3b8b9452/37523/vstack.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b1ec75b62d9ad30329f3f64d3b8b9452/e9ff0/vstack.png 180w,\n/static/b1ec75b62d9ad30329f3f64d3b8b9452/f21e7/vstack.png 360w,\n/static/b1ec75b62d9ad30329f3f64d3b8b9452/37523/vstack.png 720w,\n/static/b1ec75b62d9ad30329f3f64d3b8b9452/302a4/vstack.png 1080w,\n/static/b1ec75b62d9ad30329f3f64d3b8b9452/62da8/vstack.png 1262w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Vstack</code>은 화면 상에 보이던 안 보이던 child 뷰를 전부 로드한다. <strong>child 뷰 수가 적고 렌더링이 딜레이 되면 안 되는 상황에는 <code class=\"language-text\">Vstack</code>을 사용하자</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>예시 : 텍스트 뷰 10개를 포함한 VStack</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> body<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">some</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">View</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token class-name\">VStack</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n        alignment<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>leading<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        spacing<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token class-name\">ForEach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n            <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            id<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">self</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token class-name\">Text</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string-literal\"><span class=\"token string\">\"Item </span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">\\(</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token short-argument\">$0</span></span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token string\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 182px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 345%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Vstack-example\"\n        title=\"Vstack-example\"\n        src=\"/static/93d31b000cb6f5419689a7b765474401/a51ee/SwiftUI-VStack.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/93d31b000cb6f5419689a7b765474401/e9ff0/SwiftUI-VStack.png 180w,\n/static/93d31b000cb6f5419689a7b765474401/a51ee/SwiftUI-VStack.png 182w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 182px) 100vw, 182px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<p><a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/documentation/swiftui/vstack\">애플 공식문서 : VStack</a></p>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"-lazyvstack\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-lazyvstack\" aria-label=\" lazyvstack permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>🍔 LazyVStack</h2>\n<p>화면에 보이는 부분에서만 child 뷰를 로드해서 수직으로 보여주는 뷰</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 241.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"LazyVStack\"\n        title=\"LazyVStack\"\n        src=\"/static/5dcc18892078740c3645a97dc9a3cbfb/37523/lazyvstack.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5dcc18892078740c3645a97dc9a3cbfb/e9ff0/lazyvstack.png 180w,\n/static/5dcc18892078740c3645a97dc9a3cbfb/f21e7/lazyvstack.png 360w,\n/static/5dcc18892078740c3645a97dc9a3cbfb/37523/lazyvstack.png 720w,\n/static/5dcc18892078740c3645a97dc9a3cbfb/302a4/lazyvstack.png 1080w,\n/static/5dcc18892078740c3645a97dc9a3cbfb/061c7/lazyvstack.png 1216w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>말 그대로 Lazy해서 화면에 보이는 부분까지만 만들고 렌더링 해서 보여준다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>child 뷰가 많아서 현재 화면에서는 안 보이는 것까지 한 번에 다 로드하면 시간이 오래 걸리는 친구들은 <code class=\"language-text\">LazyVStack</code>을 사용하는가 보다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>스크롤이 엄청 긴 스크롤 뷰에 VStack을 사용하면 한 번에 모든 뷰를 로드해야 하니까 로딩 시간이 길어지는데, LazyVStack을 사용하면 스크롤을 내릴 때 보이는 만큼만 만들면 되니까 더 빠른 것 같다.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<ul>\n<li>예시 : ScrollView가 수직의 텍스트 라인들로 구성된 LazyVStack을 포함하고 있다</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token comment\">// LazyVStack 예시</span>\n\n<span class=\"token class-name\">ScrollView</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token class-name\">LazyVStack</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>alignment<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>leading<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token class-name\">ForEacH</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> id<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">self</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token class-name\">Text</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string-literal\"><span class=\"token string\">\"Row </span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">\\(</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token short-argument\">$0</span></span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token string\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 81.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"algin\"\n        title=\"algin\"\n        src=\"/static/772dc12a70288dc5605301d741d53e5a/37523/align.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/772dc12a70288dc5605301d741d53e5a/e9ff0/align.png 180w,\n/static/772dc12a70288dc5605301d741d53e5a/f21e7/align.png 360w,\n/static/772dc12a70288dc5605301d741d53e5a/37523/align.png 720w,\n/static/772dc12a70288dc5605301d741d53e5a/302a4/align.png 1080w,\n/static/772dc12a70288dc5605301d741d53e5a/07a9c/align.png 1440w,\n/static/772dc12a70288dc5605301d741d53e5a/799f3/align.png 1642w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>→ LazyVStack 사용시 스택은 스크롤뷰의 leading edge(왼쪽 모서리)에 정렬된다</p>\n<br>\n<p><a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/documentation/swiftui/lazyvstack\">애플 공식문서 : LazyVStack</a></p>\n<br>","frontmatter":{"date":"April 09, 2022","title":"VStack과 LazyVStack은 언제 사용하지? - SwiftUI","categories":"iOS","author":"콤퓨타샤","emoji":"📱"},"fields":{"slug":"/iOS-VStack-LazyVStack/"}},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://computasha.github.io","comments":{"utterances":{"repo":"compuTasha/blog-comments"}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/iOS-SafeArea/","nextSlug":"/UX-Fitts-Law/","prevSlug":"/iOS-VStack-LazyVStack/"}},
